//www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/90210-Season-2/13870 |title=90210 - Release Date, Bonus Material and More for The Complete 2nd Season |last=Lambert |first=David |website=[[TVShowsOnDVD.com]] |date=June 7, 2010 |accessdate=June 9, 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610213243/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/90210-Season-2/13870 |archivedate=June 10, 2010 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n||September 6, 2010<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B003I86LTA |title=90210 - Season Two DVD: Shenae Grimes, Jessica Stroup, Jessica Lowndes, Matt Lanter, Tristan Wilds, Michael Steger, AnnaLynne McCord: DVD |website=Amazon.co.uk |date= |accessdate=April 2, 2011}}</ref>\n||July 21, 2011<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ezydvd.com.au/item.zml/819398 |title=Buy 90210 - The 2nd Season (6 Disc Set) @ EzyDVD |website=Ezydvd.com.au |date=July 20, 2011 |accessdate=August 15, 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110819122818/http://www.ezydvd.com.au/item.zml/819398 |archivedate=August 19, 2011 |df=mdy }}</ref>\n||6\n|| Cast and Crew Commentaries on Selected Episodes; New Faces, Same Drama;<br />From the Hills to the Beach: The Look of ''90210''; Beverly Hills Surf Crew; Welcome to the Beach Club; Set Tour: Beverly Hills Beach Club; Adrianna and Navid; Looking Back: ''90210'' Season 2 in Review\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"background:#45A6AC; height:10px;\"|'''The Third Season'''\n|| August 30, 2011\n|| August 15, 2011<ref name=\"amazon1\">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B004SOPTTQ |title=<nowiki>90210 - Season 3 [DVD</nowiki>&#93;: Amazon.co.uk: Shenae Grimes, Tristan Wilds, Anna Lynne McCord: Film & TV |website=Amazon.co.uk |date= |accessdate=August 15, 2011}}</ref>\n|| July 18, 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ezydvd.com.au/DVD/90210-the-3rd-season/dp/6115689|title=90210 - The 3rd Season|work=EzyDVD|accessdate=February 22, 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815161852/http://www.